          "Code": "local playerName = player.PlayerComponent.UserId\nlocal playerData = _DataStorageService:GetUserDataStorage(playerName)\n\n-- 플레이어의 인벤토리를 저장합니다. ----------------------------\nlocal keyTable = {}\n\n--- 플레이어의 인벤토리 ID\nkeyTable[\"Iv_id\"] = _UtilLogic:TableToString(player.PlayerData.Inventory_Name)\n\n--- 플레이어의 인벤토리 Quantity\nkeyTable[\"Iv_quantity\"] = _UtilLogic:TableToString(player.PlayerData.Inventory_Quantity)\n\n\n-- ==============================================================\n-- KeyTable 저장\n-- ==============================================================\nplayerData:BatchSetAndWait(keyTable)\n",
